definition: incapable of being changed or moved or undone
details:
adjective
- incapable of being changed or moved or undone
= synonyms: frozen
- (of a number) having a fixed and unchanging value
- securely placed or fastened or set
= example: securely placed or fastened or set
- fixed and unmoving
= example: fixed and unmoving
= synonyms: rigid, set
